      <title>火锅加马力，中国车的噱头太过头了吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mixing-hotpot-with-horsepower-have-chinese-car-gimmicks-gone-too-far</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众所周知，中国汽车制造商总是敢于创新，推出新功能来吸引消费者。例如，车载卡拉 OK、可变成游戏机的方向盘以及可放平为舒适躺椅的座椅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mixing-hotpot-with-horsepower-have-chinese-car-gimmicks-gone-too-far</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从人工智能病床到远程重症监护室，初创企业正在填补印度的医疗空白</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/ai-beds-to-remotely-overseen-neonatal-icus-startups-filling-india-s-health-gaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当赛车工程师 Mudit Dandwate 的叔叔在印度一家医院因未确诊的败血症而差点丧命时，他决定将自己在赛车方面的经验应用到医疗保健领域，以改善患者监测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/ai-beds-to-remotely-overseen-neonatal-icus-startups-filling-india-s-health-gaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能需求激增 台湾暗示对核电持开放态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/taiwan-signals-openness-to-nuclear-power-amid-surging-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾行政院长赵荣泰表示，台湾“非常开放”地使用新核技术来满足芯片制造商在人工智能热潮中对电力的大量需求——这是迄今为止政府重新考虑反对核反应堆立场的最有力信号之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/taiwan-signals-openness-to-nuclear-power-amid-surging-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，Perplexity AI 在新一轮融资中寻求 80 亿美元估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/perplexity-ai-seeks-8-billion-valuation-in-new-round-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》周日报道，人工智能搜索公司 Perplexity AI 已开始融资谈判，其目标是将其估值增加一倍以上，达到 80 亿美元或以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/perplexity-ai-seeks-8-billion-valuation-in-new-round-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 20:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果新款 iPad Mini 彰显公司秘密的 AI 优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-20/apple-s-latest-ipad-mini-highlights-ai-advantage-sonos-considers-new-headphones-m2hkz4mn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果的新款 iPad mini 凸显了该公司在人工智能方面的秘密优势。此外：Sonos 在开局低迷后考虑重启耳机业务；亚马逊推出彩色 Kindle；乔纳森·艾维设计的夹克问世。在管理方面，苹果的首席人才官和顶级招聘人员离职，公司任命了新的硬件领导者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-20/apple-s-latest-ipad-mini-highlights-ai-advantage-sonos-considers-new-headphones-m2hkz4mn</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 12:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
